\c 45
\s Kuparadzaniswa kwenyika; mugove waJehovha
\p
\v 1 Zvino pamuchagova nyika nemujenya kuva nhaka, muchapa chipo kuna Jehovha, nzvimbo tsvene yenyika. Kureba kuchava kureba \add kwetsanga\add* zvuru makumi maviri nemashanu, uye kufara zvuru gumi. Iyi ichava tsvene kumuganhu wese wayo kupoteredza.
\v 2 Kune iyi kuchava nenzvimbo tsvene ine mazana mashanu pamwe nemazana mashanu, yakaenzana mativi mana akapoteredza; uye ive bani rine makubhiti makumi mashanu kupoteredza.
\v 3 Zvino nechiyero ichi muchayera, kureba kuve zvuru makumi maviri nezvishanu, uye kufara kuve zvuru gumi; nemukati mayo muchava nenzvimbo tsvene, tsvene yedzitsvene.
\v 4 Ichava nzvimbo tsvene yenyika; ichava yevapristi, vashumiri venzvimbo tsvene, vanoswedera kuti vashumire Jehovha; zvino ichava kwavari nzvimbo yedzimba, nenzvimbo tsvene yeimba tsvene.
\v 5 Zvino urefu hwezvuru makumi maviri neshanu, nekufara kwezvuru makumi maviri neshanu, VaRevhi vashumiri venzvimbo tsvene vachava nazvo, kuva nhaka, makamuri makumi maviri.
\p
\v 6 Zvino muchapa nhaka yeguta, zvuru zvishanu kufara, nezvuru makumi maviri nezvishanu kureba, mhiri pakatarisana nechipo chitsvene; ichava yeimba yese yaIsraeri.
\p
\v 7 Zvino muchinda achava nerutivi rwuno nerutivi irwo rwechipo chitsvene, nekwenhaka yeguta mberi kwechipo chitsvene, nemberi kwenhaka yeguta, kubva kurutivi rwemavirazuva wakananga kumavirazuva, uye kubva kurutivi rwemabvazuva wakananga kumabvazuva; nekureba kuchanangana neumwe wemigove, kubva pamuganhu wekumavirazuva kusvika kumuganhu wekumabvazuva.
\v 8 Maererano nenyika, uchava nayo ive nhaka kwaIsraeri; uye machinda angu haangazomanikidzizve vanhu vangu, asi achapa nyika kuimba yaIsraeri zvichienderana nemarudzi avo.
\p
\v 9 Anoreva seizvi Ishe Jehovha: Zvakwana kwandiri, imwi machinda ekwaIsraeri! Bvisai chisimba nekupamba, uye itai mutongo nekururama, mubvise kudzinga kwenyu kuvanhu vangu, anoreva Ishe Jehovha.
\v 10 Muchava nezviyero zvakarurama, neefa* yakarurama, nebhati* rakarurama.
\v 11 Efa nebhati zvichava chiyero chimwe, kuti bhati ritakure chegumi chehomeri*; neefa chegumi chehomeri, chiyero chazvo chichava chehomeri.
\v 12 Zvino shekeri richava magera* makumi maviri; mashekeri makumi maviri nemashanu, nemashekeri gumi nemashanu, achava mane* renyu.
\p
\v 13 Ichi chipo chamuchapa: Chetanhatu cheefa yehomeri chegorosi, uye muchapa chetanhatu cheefa yehomeri chebhari.
\v 14 Maererano nechimiso chemafuta, bhati remafuta, \add richapa\add* chegumi chebhati pakori*, homeri yemabhati gumi, nokuti mabhati gumi ihomeri.
\v 15 Uye gwayana rimwe paboka remakwai, pamazana maviri, panzvimbo ine mvura yaIsraeri, rive chipo chechidyiwa, uye rechipo chinopiswa, nerechipo cherugare, kuvayananisira, anoreva Ishe Jehovha.
\v 16 Vanhu vese venyika vachava pachipo ichi kuitira muchinda waIsraeri.
\v 17 Zvino zvichava pamusoro pemuchinda \add kupa\add* zvipo zvinopiswa, nezvipo zvezvidyiwa, nezvipo zvezvinwiwa, pamabiko, nepakugara kwemwedzi, nepamasabata, nepamitambo yese yakatarwa yeimba yaIsraeri. Achagadzira chipo chechivi, nechipo chechidyiwa, nechipo chinopiswa, nechipo chekuyananisa, kuyananisira imba yaIsraeri.
\p
\v 18 Anoreva seizvi Ishe Jehovha: Mu\add mwedzi\add* wekutanga, nerekutanga remwedzi, uchatora nzombe diki isina chaingapomerwa, ndokunatsa nzvimbo tsvene.
\v 19 Zvino mupristi achatora paropa rechipo chechivi, ndokuisa pamagwatidziro eimba, nepamakona mana emucheto wearitari, nepagwatidziro resuwo rechivanze chemukati.
\v 20 Zvino uchaita saizvozvo nerechinomwe remwedzi nekuda kweumwe neumwe anotadza, uye nekuda kwechituta, saizvozvo uchayananisira imba.
\v 21 Mu\add mwedzi\add* wekutanga, nezuva regumi nemana remwedzi, muchava nepasika, mabiko emazuva manomwe, chingwa chisina kuviriswa chichadyiwa.
\v 22 Nepazuva iro muchinda achazvigadzirira pamwe nevanhu vese venyika nzombe diki, chipo chechivi.
\v 23 Zvino mazuva manomwe emabiko achagadzira chipo chinopiswa kuna Jehovha, nzombe diki nomwe nemakondohwe manomwe, zvisina chazvingapomerwa zuva rimwe nerimwe, mazuva manomwe, nembudzana yembudzi zuva rimwe nerimwe, chipo chechivi.
\v 24 Zvino achagadzira chipo chechidyiwa cheefa panzombe diki, neefa pagondohwe, nehini* yemafuta paefa.
\v 25 Mu\add mwedzi\add* wechinomwe, nezuva regumi nemashanu remwedzi, uchaita sezvepamabiko emazuva manomwe, zvichienderana nechipo chechivi, zvichienderana nechipo chinopiswa, uye zvichienderana nechipo chechidyiwa, uye zvichienderana nemafuta.